{"tid":2458302,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"飛虎埋伏歷史博物館行蹤曝光 稱拍照導致理大行動延遲十多小時","createTime":"2021-03-23T10:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T11:09:24.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"64d7becb4a04841bf24ad44b0b4db7214dc29d49","tid":2458302,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T10:15:37.000Z","msg":"前年11月警方圍堵理大期間，一度派遣飛虎隊在校園附近的歷史博物館埋伏觀察，惟開始不久便以隊員行蹤曝光為由終止行動。有博物館職員被指拍攝飛虎隊員在館內執勤並把照片放上網，被控阻差辦公，案件今續審。指派警員進入博物館的總督察供稱，同袍終止勘察行動後，他直至凌晨才再派員進入館內執勤，導致驅散和拘捕理大一帶示威者的行動因而延遲了十多小時。<br />\n<br />\n總督察D在盤問下稱，案發時他在位於粉嶺的機動部隊總部執勤拒絕透露如何獲取情報。及後D在裁判官<span class=\"red\">鄭念慈</span>詢問下，始同意他接收現場資訊的渠道包括觀看直播片段。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指出，<span class=\"red\">D沒有要求警長C向館方職員指出警方行動是秘密進行。D同意此說</span>，並自言和C共事多年，C理應知道勘察行動是以絕對保密的方式進行。"},{"pid":"1bf56ee07da487f5ff323b19f756290e539647d9","tid":2458302,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T10:15:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210323/JQC3RTGX4NFNJEN5GKPEE64JO4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210323%2FJQC3RTGX4NFNJEN5GKPEE64JO4%2F&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97TcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=5c91acb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210323%2FJQC3RTGX4NFNJEN5GKPEE64JO4%2F&h=6bd0c80c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210323/JQC3RTGX4NFNJEN5GKPEE64JO4/</a>"},{"pid":"79ef8218ea23e76e61150208392fc9fde5e04a66","tid":2458302,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T10:18:01.000Z","msg":"吹大啲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0717d3a98fbf80b7a0f008c435ed83000f8b5455","tid":2458302,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T10:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75f826de318f210abde8c0eb73fb523d2c08c85","tid":2458302,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T10:19:51.000Z","msg":"吳指出，警方勘察行動早於 3 時 15 分曝光，而 D 在 3 時 40 分始看到涉案照片，故行動敗露根本與被告無關。惟 D 不同意，並謂<span class=\"red\">「我覺得佢哋（示威者）係唔會知（行動）。」</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳又指，D 在首次行動失敗後，根本不需要等到翌日凌晨始展開第二次勘察，惟他否認。吳續問，是否有人阻止他派員勘察。D 再次指涉及行動細節，不願在此透露。吳追問「你意思係有人阻止你？」D 反駁指「我無咁講過。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%B4%A9%E9%9C%B2%E9%A3%9B%E8%99%8E%E9%9A%8A%E5%8B%98%E5%AF%9F%E9%BB%9E-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%95%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E6%97%A9%E6%95%97%E9%9C%B2-%E5%8C%BF%E5%90%8D%E7%B8%BD%E7%9D%A3%E5%AF%9F%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B4%25A9%25E9%259C%25B2%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%2599%258E%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%258B%2598%25E5%25AF%259F%25E9%25BB%259E-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%25BC%2595%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%2597%25A9%25E6%2595%2597%25E9%259C%25B2-%25E5%258C%25BF%25E5%2590%258D%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%259D%25A3%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%2F&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97TcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=d14e8797\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B4%25A9%25E9%259C%25B2%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%2599%258E%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%258B%2598%25E5%25AF%259F%25E9%25BB%259E-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%25BC%2595%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%2